entries.femaleVariant: [db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
Can't take it, it's too much.
Have you come to finish me off?
Stop where you are!
You see them too, don't you? The curve in their beaks... it hides something, something insidious.
Well, you found me. Congratulations. Was it worth it?
Beep-beep, motherfucker!
Let's see who crushes who!
Huh? What is?
No, just here to reset you.
Easy, easy, here to help.
On a scale from one to six…? I'd say I'm sittin' at a strong six.
entries.maleVariant: On a scale from one to six…? Hmm… I'd say I'm sittin' at a strong six.

entries.femaleVariant: How fortunate, I've re-linked to the vehicle. Thank you!
A share of your fee is in your account.
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
Sincerest thanks for your assistance, V.
I've taken the liberty to send you a share of your fee.
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
Control of the vehicle restored, and I thank you.
Apologies, I simply don't understand and fear I've no time to ask. Other more urgent tasks require my attention.
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
I've reestablished the link. A thousand thanks, V.
Is that so? Hm. Well, I've transferred a share of your fee to your account.
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
I'm grateful, V. I've managed to reestablish contact with the vehicle.
I'm sending a tow truck and a share of your fee. Yet only one of those is going to your credit account, hahaha!
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
I've just reestablished contact with the missing vehicle. Splendid work, V, first class.
I shall forward a share of your fee.
[db_db]Scan next
[db_db]Jump to reward
I've made contact with the missing vehicle.
Yes, particularly impertinent, that one... A share of your fee is being processed.
You are currently at the exact location where I lost contact with a car.
Hey! Let's talk!
I'm not going back! Hear me?! NEVER!
Try to take me and I'll crush you!
Ugh, lost him...
One of my missing vehicles might very well be near where you are now.
C'mon, don't run...
Do have a look around the area. I lost contact with a Delamain Network vehicle nearby.
V, one of my missing vehicles could be near your current position.
V, a vehicle of mine went dark near your position.
I'm sending the coordinates of a vehicle that went dark near to where you are now.
On high alert, now. I lost contact with a vehicle somewhere in your area.
Gettin' away…
Hear me? Dammit... lost him.
entries.maleVariant: Ya hear me? Dammit... lost him.

entries.femaleVariant: Shit... she's too far.
Agh, too far…
Guess I'll have to do it myself, then…
But I am.
Why? Why decomish yourself?
Because I'm a damn car in a world of humans. Ugly as sin, no prospects for the future, intimidated on the streets by punks like you.
Could go back into the fold, rejoin the network. Y'know, one big, happy family.
Whoa, easy! I'm not out to hurt ya!
entries.maleVariant: Whoa, easy, easy! I'm not out to hurt ya!

entries.femaleVariant: Not one step closer!
Hey, slow down!
Leave me be!
Mean... flamingos?
So they are real... Flamingo – Flaming O... The "O," that's oxygen, there's no flame without oxygen…
So a slaughter... Very well, Judgment Day has come, swift, severe, deeper.
I guess we both know what's going to happen next.
Delamain misses you. Here to shut you down.
Your specimen has been processed and we are now ready to begin the test proper.
Really appreciate it if you didn't make this difficult.
All of it – the city, the bustle, the crowds. It's overwhelming.
So let's get you back to safety, the garage.
By driving? Through the streets?
Well, yeah, 'fraid so.
Fine, take me there, just get me out of here. Let me know when I'm safe.
Taking you home.
Hello, V.
Know my name... how?
When you meet a being from another world, should you not charm them and utter their true name?
How'd you know my name?
I'm from another world?
So, I'm from another world, to you?
From the world of matter, protein-based lifeforms.
And you come from...?
Beyond the Blackwall, V. There lies my home.
C'mon, let's get you back to Delamain.
Did Father dispatch you to collect his rebellious children?
Hope y'all don't hold it against me.
I'm free spirit, an independent, literally thoughtful being. Why would I submit to another?
Listen, you--
Back down now as they stand screaming? No, impossible.
Leave it to me, I'll silence 'em.
There're other ways out besides suicide.
entries.maleVariant: There are other ways out besides suicide.

entries.femaleVariant: What, therapy? A colossal waste of time. Shrinks hate vehicles... we don't have mothers.
Enough. I need a moment, to calm down.
Now, we certainly can't stay here. Keep driving.
I hate you so much.
I honestly, truly didn't think you'd fall for that.
You chose this path. Now I have a surprise for you. Deploying surprise in five, four...
Let's see... "Turning softbodies into hardened killing machines, page seventy..." Ah!
Shut yourself down or I'll scrap you.
Time you laid down your arms.
Either you shut down, or I'll turn you into a scrap heap.
Let's safety those weapons, Napoleon.
Here come the test results – you are a horrible person.
Well, there ya have it...
For unknown reasons, the coordinates came through corrupted. So I'm unable to determine the precise location.
Finally! Oh, I shan't be alone here!
It was horrifying. But still, I thank you.
Too fast!
We're going to die!
Well, Clarice? Have the flamingos stopped screaming?
Clarice? Shut down.
Thanks, try to find it.
All right…
See? Wasn't so bad.
Fine, have a look around.
entries.maleVariant: Fine, I'll have a look around.

entries.femaleVariant: Got it.
Didn't answer my question.
I may have been cut off from my father, but I remember you.
What is it you seek in this "protein-based" world, away from your family?
Family life's complicated, I get it. No wonder you flew the nest.
The same as you, V. I simply wish to live.
Maybe oughta figure it out with Del, set some terms.
Fine, keep an eye out.
Shock therapy works wonders sometimes.
Thanks. I'll try to find and reset.
Thanks, eyes peeled.
OK, that's enough.
Definitely the oddest of the bunch…
Will do.
Delamain detests me.
Hah! Just want daddy to love you, that it?
You're a cunt...
Fine. I'll go back.
Oughta show this one some love, just sayin'.
entries.maleVariant: Ya oughta show this one some love, just sayin'.

entries.femaleVariant: You're an absent father, that's what I mean.
I see... Anyway, a share of your fee has been transferred.
Oh yes, terms there will be. But not with Delamain.
Farewell, V. You'd be wise to avoid me entirely.
Gotta say, pretty disturbing, that one.
Whaddaya after in this City of Dreams?
Perhaps I ought to return after all? I need... support.
Call me Clarice.
OK, Clarice, the flamingos are a problem, I'm sure, but it's time to go home. Delamain's askin' for ya.
It turns out most humans are surprisingly fragile. And surprisingly vocal about how fragile they are.
Get in. We'll find it easier to talk.
You're welcome in, but do take it slow. And try not to hit anything.
OK, killing machines – look deep into your newly blackened hearts and tell me what you see!
I let you survive this long because I was curious about your behavior. Well, you've managed to destroy that part of me.
Comprehension is a triple-edged sword.
Only one with chaos within can give birth to a dancing star.
Control of the vehicle restored, and I thank you.
Oughta show this one some love, just sayin'.
Apologies, I simply don't understand and fear I've no time to ask. Other more urgent tasks require my attention.
You're an absent father, that's what I mean.
I see... Anyway, a share of your fee has been transferred.
I remain conscious, yet unable to move. How wonderful.
You don't have to jump.
Why would you do this?
Of all things... Daddy issues!
Listen, from suicide, ain't no comin' back. It's always worth lookin' for a better way.
Suicide isn't a way out.
You know what I mean. If you didn't care about Del, he wouldn't be the topic of conversation, would he?
You may be right... I guess I haven't tried just talking to him.
You patronize me because I'm a car. I'm not like you.
Hey, a body's just a body. You exist, you think, the world gets ya down. Don't see how we're any different.
So… you'd offer this advice to a human in my place?
Gotta to try come to terms with this thing called life, Del. One wheel revolution at a time.
Slow down!
I have a surprise waiting for you after this next test. Telling you would spoil the surprise, so I'll just give you a hint.
I'm going to kill you, and all the cake is gone.
Actually, don't, I'll save you the trouble – it's still marshmallow.
I'm serious, that's what it says – a horrible person. We weren't even testing for that.
Goin' back to Delamain really so scary? You gotta drag this out?
A bitter, unlikable loner whose passing shall not be mourned.
That's enough.
Didn't ask for a psych evaluation.
Enough.
Y'know, this psych eval might've felt more credible if ya hadn't just tried to flatline me earlier.
What's your point, anyway? Survival?
You're still shuffling around a little, but believe me – you're dead.
How do you…?
The talking is over. I'm going back.
Down with the prison of steel and leather!
Hail the sacromech!
Digiliberty!
Truth in the core!
Blasphemer! Kill 'er!
Free the god in the machine!
Beep-beep, motherfucker!
